 419	- **Controller Binding**: @FXML annotations bind UI components to controller fields
 420	- **Event Handling**: FXML onAction attributes link to controller methods
 421	- **CSS Styling**: External stylesheet integration for consistent UI theming
 422	- **Resource Management**: Resources loaded from classpath with proper module access
