 26	- **Compiler**: Java 21 source and target compatibility
 27	- **Packaging**: Modular JAR with jlink support for native packaging
 28	- **Dependencies**: Centralized dependency management with version control
 29	
 30	#### Apache POI 5.4.1 Integration
 31	- **Excel Processing**: XLSX file import/export functionality
 32	- **Workbook Management**: XSSFWorkbook for Excel 2007+ format support
 33	- **Data Mapping**: Customer entity to Excel cell mapping
 34	- **Error Handling**: Comprehensive import/export error tracking
 35	
 36	#### JasperReports 6.20.6 Integration
 37	- **Report Engine**: JasperReports with reflection-based implementation
 38	- **Template System**: JRXML template files for report design
 39	- **Export Formats**: PDF export with file chooser integration
 40	- **Data Source**: JRBeanCollectionDataSource for customer data
